headline: Q2 Earnings Roundup: IDEX (NYSE:IEX) And The Rest Of The Gas and Liquid Handling Segment
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q2. Today, we are looking at gas and liquid handling stocks, starting with IDEX (NYSE:IEX).
